perfSONAR_PS::Client::Echo README File
======================================

Description
-----------

perfSONAR_PS::Client::Echo is a module that provides an OO interface to perform
perfSONAR ping requests against perfSONAR services.

Installation
------------

 CPAN installation
 -----------------

    perl -MCPAN -e 'install perfSONAR_PS::Client::Echo'

 Standard installation
 ---------------------

    Prerequisites:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

